{"title":"洪水中的家园","authors":["廖志理"],"dates":[{"year":1996,"month":8,"day":17}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"洪水中的家园"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"廖志理"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"洪水洪水"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这被大雨鞭打的咆哮"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这被闷雷驱赶的波涛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"窜过了千年的堤防！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"稻子秧苗房梁炊烟"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"被大水淹没的家园"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"被大水冲走的哭喊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那浪花卷走的兄弟不再回来！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在即将冲垮的大堤"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有人在抬石有人在筑垒"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在临时搭成的窝棚里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有人在生火：水中不灭的火光！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这不是命运却是灾难"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让我们垒土打桩"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在地上打桩在心上打桩"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用信念的桩扎住泛滥的悲伤！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":7,"page_end":7}